rComments: His lectures are hilarious! He has jokes to help us understand the concepts better which I loved! The way he makes his slides is the best I've ever seen, he puts the slides with all the information except for a few missing words and he tells you those words as the lecture goes on, all you need to do is study the slides. His exams are fair and easy!

I really loved this class!!! A lot of material and it's better not to miss class, but Mr. Laurin is pretty entertaining (funny) and that made me want to attend. Content can be a bit tricky at times, and exams are not super easy, but he explains the content well, so if you are serious, you will do well for sure. Overall, great guy!

Super prof. Passionné par sa matière, heureux de voir les élèves réussir. Très facile d'avoir de bonnes notes en allant au cours. Cours magistral dynamique, drôle, facile à comprendre et à suivre. Examens faciles si on est allé aux cours, on a étudié un peu et on a une compréhension générale de la matière. Je reprendrais ce prof n'importe quand!

Patrick uses a lot of pop culture references to teach the material and he's quite funny. Very enjoyable lectures- first midterm was extremely hard and class average was very low. He took feedback well and 2nd midterm was much better. Exam was basically a third midterm- short and sweet. Great prof; will take him again if he teaches other classes
Amazing prof. Must attend class but if you do you're guaranteed a decent grade. Very memorable.

Course was fine. Attend class because although he does post his slides, half of the information in them is missing. Dont bother with the readings (only 3 MC questions about them on each. test).The first midterm was hard but the second one and exam were very very easy! He's funny but class can be a little dull at times. Go to class & you'll be fine!
Excellent prof! Des lectures très intéressante et facile à suivre. Je le recommande fortement!

Prof très très intéressant, passionné par sa matière. C'est mieux de ne pas manquer de cours, parce que les powerpoints qu'il met sur Brightspace ont des trous qui sont remplis en classe. Vraiment drôle, et si vous prenez son cours, espérez qu'il fasse un podcast ou un cours en ligne, c'est remplis de blagues et de niaiseries.

Super prof! Sa matière lui tient à coeur et ça paraît. Il est drôle et il nous garde réveillé. Ses examens sont assez faciles, mais c mieux de ne pas manquer de cours. Il explique très bien aussi. Je le recommande vraiment et je vais changer de programme à cause de lui!

Best prof I have had since starting uni! Classes are super entertaining, funny, well structured and laid back. He also takes time to explain complex ideas to make sure that we really understand (really good at explaining). Exams aren't super easy, but if you study, you can do super well because there are no catches. I hope he teaches other classes!

He's a really great prof! He makes his lectures as entertaining and fun for the students. His slides have a lot of visuals and are simple to follow. He's definitely not a boring or stiff prof. Would definitely take a second course with him!

Never take his class, exams are extremely hard and there's only three a semester. When reading over the material for the class it could be much more simply put but he's very wordy and phrases questions on exams terribly.
